Title: Repeals article 21 of the economic development law relating to the "START-UP NY program"
Summary: Relates to the "SUNY Tax-free Areas to Revitalize and Transform UPstate New York program," or the "START-UP NY program".
ActClause: AN ACT to repeal article 21 of the economic development law relating to the "SUNY Tax-free Areas to Revitalize and Transform UPstate New York program", or the "START-UP NY program"
